# sn-api-helper-mcp

MCP server for SignNow API helper tools (stdio only).

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Run

```bash
python -m sn_api_helper_mcp serve
```

or

```bash
sn-api-helper-mcp serve
```

## Features

- Transport: stdio only
- Tools: `get_signnow_api_info` - Get information about SignNow API
